| Operator | Description        | Example       |
| -------- | ------------------ | ------------- |
| `+`      | Addition           | `2 + 3` â†’ `5` |
| `-`      | Subtraction        | `5 - 2` â†’ `3` |
| `*`      | Multiplication     | `2 * 3` â†’ `6` |
| `/`      | Division           | `6 / 2` â†’ `3` |
| `%`      | Modulo (remainder) | `5 % 2` â†’ `1` |

âœ… Example: All Together
In prod, it creates 2 large instances
In dev, 1 small instance

variable "env" {
  default = "dev"
}

resource "aws_instance" "web" {
  count         = var.env == "prod" ? 2 : 1
  ami           = "ami-123456"
  instance_type = var.env == "prod" ? "t3.large" : "t3.micro"

  tags = {
    Environment = var.env
  }
}

